Pedipalp
. Without apophyses; trochanter with sharply produced ventro-distal extension, ventral margin with ca. 8 (
♂
), 7 (
♀
) stout setae, without mesal spur; tarsus and tibia without spines; tarsal spur present; claw 0.7 (
♂
) × length of tarsus.

Abdomen
